Version 0.0.1
-----------------------------------------
Zumron is a php driven project.

You can add your favorite Usenet tools to this page.

Things you need to have installed before installation of zumron
Apache2 
php5.3
github


--- Installation ---

Basic apache2 + php5.3 installation 

Goto /var/www/
git clone https://github.com/rudie2004/Zumron.git

Or 

Unpack in a directory where your webserver is running.

--- Configuration ---

Goto the folder components then topmenu and edit the config.php page.